cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with adversarial attacks and defenses in image classification, which are topics commonly studied in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a new defense method using randomized smoothing, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
